1
00:00:00,060 --> 00:00:05,100
♪ Inside the state a city is built ♪

2
00:00:05,100 --> 00:00:10,220
♪ Where a benevolent emperor resides ♪

3
00:00:10,220 --> 00:00:15,380
♪ Court officials are brave and able ♪

4
00:00:15,380 --> 00:00:22,780
♪ The empress is fair ♪

5
00:00:25,620 --> 00:00:30,740
♪ Princes died too young to ascend the throne ♪

6
00:00:30,740 --> 00:00:35,620
♪ Princesses are spoiled and fragile ♪

7
00:00:35,860 --> 00:00:40,300
♪ Commoners are also the emperor’s children ♪

8
00:00:40,860 --> 00:00:49,660
♪ All are living peacefully ♪

9
00:00:49,980 --> 00:00:54,300
♪ Wish I could live a day for myself ♪

10
00:00:55,020 --> 00:00:59,420
♪ Follow my heart and ethics without distractions ♪

11
00:01:00,740 --> 00:01:03,420
♪ To be a good husband ♪

12
00:01:03,420 --> 00:01:06,020
♪ To be a caring father ♪

13
00:01:06,500 --> 00:01:10,140
♪ We were close when we first met ♪

14
00:01:10,500 --> 00:01:14,740
♪ I hope I can control my desires ♪

15
00:01:15,580 --> 00:01:20,100
♪ To be a worriless emperor and father ♪

16
00:01:21,140 --> 00:01:23,900
♪ Prudence tops all virtues ♪

17
00:01:23,900 --> 00:01:26,500
♪ People build the state ♪

18
00:01:26,780 --> 00:01:30,020
= Held in the Lonely Castle =
♪ May the world be peaceful ♪

19
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:32,980
= Episode 61 =

20
00:01:33,340 --> 00:01:34,620
I’ll be back after I finish buying those gifts.

21
00:01:34,900 --> 00:01:36,460
Princess! Princess!

22
00:01:41,540 --> 00:01:42,940
Jiaqing Zi must have something funny

23
00:01:42,940 --> 00:01:43,820
to tell you.

24
00:01:44,500 --> 00:01:45,420
I shall take my leave

25
00:01:45,660 --> 00:01:46,900
and let you two talk.

26
00:01:50,140 --> 00:01:50,980
They said

27
00:01:51,220 --> 00:01:52,140
Mrs. Yang

28
00:01:52,140 --> 00:01:54,300
was crying and tearing her hair.

29
00:01:54,620 --> 00:01:55,380
Prince Consort

30
00:01:55,380 --> 00:01:56,980
was repeating himself over and over again.

31
00:01:57,220 --> 00:01:58,980
And he got a large bump on his forehead.

32
00:02:00,820 --> 00:02:02,660
They can do whatever they like.

33
00:02:02,900 --> 00:02:04,100
Just don’t do it in front of me.

34
00:02:04,420 --> 00:02:05,220
I don’t care.

35
00:02:05,940 --> 00:02:08,100
= Jiaqing Zi =

36
00:02:08,100 --> 00:02:09,500
Prince Consort is very determined.

37
00:02:09,940 --> 00:02:12,220
Seems he’s not like his mother.

38
00:02:15,100 --> 00:02:17,460
I don’t care what kind of person he is.

39
00:02:18,460 --> 00:02:19,900
I just want him to stay away from me.

40
00:02:21,300 --> 00:02:23,700
I’ll do what I can

41
00:02:24,260 --> 00:02:25,780
to bring honor to his family.

42
00:02:35,140 --> 00:02:38,260
= Liang Yuansheng =

43
00:02:40,140 --> 00:02:40,980
Manager Liu,

44
00:02:42,020 --> 00:02:43,540
what new pens have you got?

45
00:02:44,860 --> 00:02:45,580
Mr. Liang,

46
00:02:45,580 --> 00:02:46,980
is there a special type that you like?

47
00:02:47,540 --> 00:02:48,660
Don’t you know me?

48
00:02:48,740 --> 00:02:49,980
I’m nearly illiterate.

49
00:02:50,100 --> 00:02:50,900
What can I possibly know about pens?

50
00:02:51,580 --> 00:02:53,900
I just want to buy some for my younger brother.

51
00:02:55,300 --> 00:02:56,460
You have a younger brother?

52
00:02:57,300 --> 00:02:58,180
I never heard that before.

53
00:02:59,900 --> 00:03:01,580
My younger brother’s name is Liang Yuanheng.

54
00:03:02,300 --> 00:03:03,380
My father and grandmother passed away

55
00:03:03,620 --> 00:03:05,780
not long after he was born.

56
00:03:06,980 --> 00:03:08,340
My mother took him to our hometown.

57
00:03:09,140 --> 00:03:10,260
When he was nine,

58
00:03:10,260 --> 00:03:11,340
my mother died of illness,

59
00:03:11,820 --> 00:03:12,860
and then he went lost.

60
00:03:15,700 --> 00:03:16,420
Manager Xie,

61
00:03:16,700 --> 00:03:17,740
I’ll go look around.

62
00:03:17,740 --> 00:03:18,620
But recently,

63
00:03:19,180 --> 00:03:20,980
I found him.

64
00:03:21,940 --> 00:03:23,660
Congratulations to you.

65
00:03:28,940 --> 00:03:30,900
Mister, you look like

66
00:03:31,660 --> 00:03:33,140
an old friend of mine very much.

67
00:03:38,420 --> 00:03:39,420
Don’t call me mister.

68
00:03:41,140 --> 00:03:42,300
Then what should I call you?

69
00:03:53,780 --> 00:03:55,060
Why hasn’t he returned yet?

70
00:03:57,100 --> 00:03:57,860
Princess,

71
00:04:00,420 --> 00:04:01,900
the dinner is ready.

72
00:04:03,700 --> 00:04:06,580
Prince Consort has been waiting for a while.

73
00:04:09,380 --> 00:04:10,420
Let him eat first.

74
00:04:13,100 --> 00:04:15,780
Princess, maybe Huaiji will come back

75
00:04:15,980 --> 00:04:17,260
when you finish dinner.

76
00:04:18,260 --> 00:04:19,700
He needs to buy so many things

77
00:04:19,940 --> 00:04:21,100
for His Majesty,

78
00:04:21,380 --> 00:04:22,980
Her Highness and Madam Miao...

79
00:04:48,980 --> 00:04:50,060
Open the door now!

80
00:04:51,380 --> 00:04:52,140
Right.

81
00:04:52,140 --> 00:04:53,740
It won’t be so stuffy inside then.

82
00:05:24,020 --> 00:05:24,780
Princess,

83
00:05:25,220 --> 00:05:27,620
are you feeling unwell?

84
00:05:28,340 --> 00:05:31,500
Should I call a physician to check on you?

85
00:05:38,020 --> 00:05:38,860
Princess,

86
00:05:40,500 --> 00:05:42,900
are you feeling unwell?

87
00:05:44,900 --> 00:05:47,060
Should I call a physician to check on you?

88
00:05:54,620 --> 00:05:55,700
You hit the tree again?

89
00:05:59,020 --> 00:06:01,060
You can actually

90
00:06:02,060 --> 00:06:03,380
call a physician to come now.

91
00:06:04,620 --> 00:06:05,940
Go to bedroom and lie down.

92
00:06:06,220 --> 00:06:07,660
You’re so badly injured.

93
00:06:07,980 --> 00:06:09,260
You should get some good rest.

94
00:06:10,700 --> 00:06:11,620
Just don’t come to

95
00:06:11,700 --> 00:06:13,220
eat with me in the next few days.

96
00:06:15,580 --> 00:06:17,380
Jiaqing Zi, be quick.

97
00:06:17,900 --> 00:06:19,300
Send him back.

98
00:06:20,580 --> 00:06:22,580
Call a physician to take a look at him.

99
00:07:11,060 --> 00:07:12,460
You can’t force me to go with you.

100
00:07:13,100 --> 00:07:15,420
I said I’ve something urgent to do.

101
00:07:22,380 --> 00:07:24,020
If you don’t let me get off,

102
00:07:24,020 --> 00:07:24,620
I’ll...

103
00:07:24,620 --> 00:07:26,220
Brother, take care of yourself.

104
00:07:29,700 --> 00:07:31,020
Don’t work too hard.

105
00:07:34,300 --> 00:07:35,540
Mother and I are good.

106
00:07:36,420 --> 00:07:38,060
Our store runs smoothly.

107
00:07:40,540 --> 00:07:42,060
Uncle also treats us well.

108
00:07:43,980 --> 00:07:45,540
Don’t worry about us,

109
00:07:46,900 --> 00:07:48,420
and stop sending money to us.

110
00:07:51,780 --> 00:07:53,540
My teacher offered me a tuition waiver

111
00:07:55,180 --> 00:07:56,660
and a part-time job

112
00:07:57,060 --> 00:07:58,220
as a transcriber.

113
00:07:59,420 --> 00:08:03,500
So I can also earn some money.

114
00:08:06,220 --> 00:08:07,420
My teacher also said

115
00:08:08,700 --> 00:08:10,940
I’ll be qualified to take the exam next year.

116
00:08:12,620 --> 00:08:14,540
I’ll study very hard,

117
00:08:17,900 --> 00:08:19,180
so that we can get together sooner.

118
00:08:26,740 --> 00:08:28,220
I’m not good at memorizing books.

119
00:08:31,620 --> 00:08:33,980
I can’t memorize anything

120
00:08:35,140 --> 00:08:36,940
that’s not about business.

121
00:08:40,780 --> 00:08:41,660
But I can remember

122
00:08:41,660 --> 00:08:43,500
every word in the letters

123
00:08:46,300 --> 00:08:47,820
my younger brother wrote to me.

124
00:09:06,780 --> 00:09:07,660
Thank you, miss.

125
00:09:11,100 --> 00:09:13,860
I’m just a maid.

126
00:09:14,220 --> 00:09:15,260
You’re my master.

127
00:09:16,140 --> 00:09:17,620
Please don’t be so polite to me.

128
00:09:22,420 --> 00:09:23,660
You can go back and get some rest.

129
00:09:25,020 --> 00:09:26,700
Princess ordered me to call a physician.

130
00:09:27,420 --> 00:09:28,900
I’ll leave after the physician

131
00:09:29,380 --> 00:09:30,740
arrives here.

132
00:09:32,020 --> 00:09:32,980
I’m fine.

133
00:09:36,220 --> 00:09:37,540
I didn’t hit the tree.

134
00:09:38,380 --> 00:09:39,060
I just...

135
00:09:40,900 --> 00:09:41,700
I know.

136
00:09:42,980 --> 00:09:44,060
You’re a very good person.

137
00:09:44,620 --> 00:09:45,740
And you treat Princess very well.

138
00:09:49,220 --> 00:09:49,900
Oh right,

139
00:09:50,100 --> 00:09:51,460
Huirou didn’t look very well

140
00:09:51,460 --> 00:09:52,180
today.

141
00:09:52,340 --> 00:09:53,700
Was she feeling unwell?

142
00:09:55,140 --> 00:09:55,860
Princess

143
00:09:57,460 --> 00:09:58,420
is fine.

144
00:09:59,100 --> 00:10:00,180
She was annoyed by the sparrows

145
00:10:00,180 --> 00:10:01,580
when she was taking a nap at noon.

146
00:10:01,580 --> 00:10:02,580
That’s why.

147
00:10:05,900 --> 00:10:06,700
Alright.

148
00:10:16,900 --> 00:10:18,660
You can go inside and take a rest.

149
00:10:19,500 --> 00:10:20,340
I’ll leave

150
00:10:20,340 --> 00:10:21,620
after I clean the table.

151
00:10:23,980 --> 00:10:25,140
That’s not necessary.

152
00:10:57,700 --> 00:11:00,860
His Majesty said you paint very well.

153
00:11:03,060 --> 00:11:03,940
I thought

154
00:11:05,060 --> 00:11:06,980
he was just praising you before Princess.

155
00:11:09,900 --> 00:11:12,300
I’m a very mediocre painter.

156
00:11:13,940 --> 00:11:15,300
I dare not make a comment on this painting.

157
00:11:16,820 --> 00:11:18,180
But I understand what it means.

158
00:11:19,860 --> 00:11:21,900
It’s a reflection of what you saw.

159
00:11:23,620 --> 00:11:24,780
As long as Princess is there,

160
00:11:26,060 --> 00:11:27,300
the rest part of the world

161
00:11:28,140 --> 00:11:30,300
will become blurry in your eyes.

162
00:11:31,420 --> 00:11:33,100
The only thing that

163
00:11:34,500 --> 00:11:35,700
you’ll ever see

164
00:11:37,420 --> 00:11:39,100
is Princess’s smile.

165
00:12:21,340 --> 00:12:22,300
It’s already dark.

166
00:12:25,220 --> 00:12:25,940
Princess.

167
00:12:27,460 --> 00:12:29,220
It’s dark. Please go inside and take a rest.

168
00:12:31,460 --> 00:12:32,420
It’s already dark.

169
00:12:33,300 --> 00:12:34,780
Why hasn’t Huaiji come back yet?

170
00:12:43,300 --> 00:12:44,020
Are you full?

171
00:12:44,020 --> 00:12:44,900
Yeah. I’m full.

172
00:12:45,340 --> 00:12:46,180
Come again.

173
00:12:46,180 --> 00:12:46,940
Alright.

174
00:12:55,180 --> 00:12:57,820
I thought you’ll take me to Winehouse Fan.

175
00:13:15,700 --> 00:13:18,740
Mother sold this yard back then.

176
00:13:21,380 --> 00:13:22,460
I swore to

177
00:13:23,620 --> 00:13:25,340
work hard as an apprentice

178
00:13:26,740 --> 00:13:28,020
and make enough money

179
00:13:30,420 --> 00:13:31,500
to buy it back,

180
00:13:34,220 --> 00:13:35,700
and get you and mother back here

181
00:13:38,580 --> 00:13:41,940
so that we can live together.

182
00:13:45,020 --> 00:13:46,340
I’m sure father and grandmother in heaven

183
00:13:46,340 --> 00:13:47,380
would be very happy

184
00:13:49,180 --> 00:13:50,580
to see this.

185
00:14:33,260 --> 00:14:35,000
= Late Father Liang Shangwen, Late Grandfather Liang Jinzhong =
= Late Grandmother Mrs. Zhang, Late Mother Mrs. Wang =

186
00:14:35,020 --> 00:14:36,620
I know

187
00:14:38,180 --> 00:14:39,940
what’s done can’t be undone.

188
00:14:43,580 --> 00:14:45,580
I didn’t want to force you to come with me.

189
00:14:47,980 --> 00:14:49,140
I just wanted to

190
00:14:50,180 --> 00:14:51,980
fulfill my long-harbored dream

191
00:14:54,780 --> 00:14:58,580
to let father, mother and grandmother

192
00:15:02,580 --> 00:15:04,580
see that I’ve found my younger brother,

193
00:15:08,820 --> 00:15:10,740
and to let my younger brother stay

194
00:15:13,260 --> 00:15:14,580
in the room I prepared for one night.

195
00:15:49,740 --> 00:15:50,580
Mother.

196
00:16:21,700 --> 00:16:23,620
My goodness, you’re finally back.

197
00:16:24,900 --> 00:16:25,940
You’ve been waiting for me?

198
00:16:25,980 --> 00:16:26,820
What happened?

199
00:16:27,780 --> 00:16:29,260
You didn’t come back yesterday afternoon.

200
00:16:29,260 --> 00:16:30,340
Princess was very anxious.

201
00:16:30,460 --> 00:16:31,380
When it got dark,

202
00:16:31,380 --> 00:16:32,780
she came to wait for you by the gate.

203
00:16:32,820 --> 00:16:33,980
We couldn’t persuade her to go inside.

204
00:16:34,020 --> 00:16:35,660
But thanks to Mr. Liang and Aunt Han,

205
00:16:35,660 --> 00:16:36,820
they said

206
00:16:37,100 --> 00:16:38,740
they would send people to look for you,

207
00:16:38,740 --> 00:16:40,180
only then did she agree to go inside.

208
00:16:40,420 --> 00:16:41,980
Later you sent a message saying

209
00:16:41,980 --> 00:16:42,940
you were not coming back

210
00:16:42,940 --> 00:16:44,020
last night,

211
00:16:44,020 --> 00:16:44,980
she felt a little relieved.

212
00:16:44,980 --> 00:16:46,460
But she became more worried very soon.

213
00:16:46,820 --> 00:16:48,820
Because you didn’t say when you’ll come back.

214
00:16:49,180 --> 00:16:50,500
She didn’t go to sleep till midnight.

215
00:16:50,620 --> 00:16:51,860
She was worried about you

216
00:16:51,860 --> 00:16:53,730
and mad at you at the same time.

217
00:16:53,820 --> 00:16:54,860
She became very anxious,

218
00:16:54,860 --> 00:16:56,340
and burst into tears.

219
00:17:09,380 --> 00:17:10,740
You have a place to stay outside,

220
00:17:11,060 --> 00:17:12,140
why bother coming back?

221
00:17:13,860 --> 00:17:14,740
Kick him out!

222
00:17:22,700 --> 00:17:23,860
Didn’t you hear me?

223
00:17:25,980 --> 00:17:27,060
Kick him out now!

224
00:17:43,500 --> 00:17:44,260
What’s this?

225
00:17:46,820 --> 00:17:48,620
This is roasted pork belly

226
00:17:48,620 --> 00:17:50,660
sold by the shop near the Great Xiangguo Temple.

227
00:17:54,260 --> 00:17:56,540
I was actually selecting gifts

228
00:17:56,540 --> 00:17:58,060
near the Great Xiangguo Temple.

229
00:17:59,020 --> 00:18:01,420
After I bought an inkstone,

230
00:18:02,460 --> 00:18:03,420
a painting,

231
00:18:03,700 --> 00:18:05,660
and an embroidered outfit,

232
00:18:06,300 --> 00:18:07,260
it was already dark.

233
00:18:08,300 --> 00:18:10,900
Then I remembered you mentioned

234
00:18:11,660 --> 00:18:13,020
you want to eat roasted pork belly.

235
00:18:13,820 --> 00:18:15,900
So I decided to buy a serving for you

236
00:18:16,420 --> 00:18:17,940
while it’s the freshest in the morning.

237
00:18:18,780 --> 00:18:21,100
You see? So I went there

238
00:18:21,300 --> 00:18:22,420
before dawn today,

239
00:18:23,180 --> 00:18:24,540
and bought the first serving

240
00:18:25,300 --> 00:18:26,700
they made.

241
00:19:10,020 --> 00:19:10,860
Why are you smirking?

242
00:19:12,740 --> 00:19:13,620
Get out.

243
00:19:35,300 --> 00:19:37,740
I stayed outside

244
00:19:38,300 --> 00:19:39,860
without your permission,

245
00:19:41,740 --> 00:19:45,100
and made you worried.

246
00:19:45,780 --> 00:19:47,020
I acknowledge my guilt.

247
00:19:48,140 --> 00:19:48,980
I know

248
00:19:51,740 --> 00:19:52,900
I made a mistake.

249
00:19:54,540 --> 00:19:56,020
I swear I won’t

250
00:19:56,620 --> 00:19:57,940
do this again in the future.

251
00:20:00,420 --> 00:20:01,580
No matter what,

252
00:20:01,780 --> 00:20:04,700
this won’t happen again.

253
00:20:49,580 --> 00:20:50,380
Your Majesty!

254
00:20:51,020 --> 00:20:51,700
Your Majesty!

255
00:20:52,260 --> 00:20:53,620
The ten of us are very sure that

256
00:20:53,740 --> 00:20:55,660
Lady of Wenxi County is pregnant.

257
00:20:55,980 --> 00:21:00,460
- The Physicians have confirmed that Lady of Wenxi County is pregnant.
- This is great!

258
00:21:00,460 --> 00:21:01,220
= Madam Dong =

259
00:21:02,220 --> 00:21:03,100
This is really great!

260
00:21:03,100 --> 00:21:04,260
Congratulations, Your Majesty!

261
00:21:04,380 --> 00:21:06,020
Lady of Wenxi County

262
00:21:06,020 --> 00:21:07,220
saved you before,

263
00:21:07,500 --> 00:21:09,420
and now she’s pregnant.

264
00:21:09,620 --> 00:21:10,820
She’s really a lucky charm

265
00:21:10,820 --> 00:21:12,220
sent to you by Heaven.

266
00:21:12,380 --> 00:21:13,140
Right.

267
00:21:15,460 --> 00:21:16,580
I hope so.

268
00:21:20,420 --> 00:21:21,940
Go prepare the sacrificial rites.

269
00:21:22,580 --> 00:21:24,140
And take stock of

270
00:21:24,140 --> 00:21:25,340
the golden and silk items in the treasury

271
00:21:25,340 --> 00:21:26,500
for future use.

272
00:21:26,700 --> 00:21:27,860
Also, go to the Cabinet.

273
00:21:27,860 --> 00:21:28,660
See if there are Prime Ministers,

274
00:21:29,100 --> 00:21:31,020
and which scholar is on duty tonight.

275
00:21:31,020 --> 00:21:31,780
Hurry!

276
00:21:40,700 --> 00:21:43,020
Lady of Wenxi County was pregnant a month ago,

277
00:21:43,060 --> 00:21:45,420
and now Lady of Anding County is also pregnant.

278
00:21:45,580 --> 00:21:47,380
All the officials have come to congratulate you.

279
00:21:47,580 --> 00:21:49,500
They said this is a blessing for you

280
00:21:49,500 --> 00:21:50,580
and our country.

281
00:21:51,500 --> 00:21:53,740
This is a blessed reward from Heaven

282
00:21:53,860 --> 00:21:55,500
for your benevolence towards the people.

283
00:21:57,780 --> 00:21:58,700
I want to

284
00:21:59,060 --> 00:22:01,260
renovate the office building the late Emperor used

285
00:22:01,380 --> 00:22:04,620
in Kaifeng Municipal Government
when he was the magistrate there

286
00:22:04,740 --> 00:22:06,260
and name it Hidden Dragon Palace

287
00:22:06,980 --> 00:22:09,340
so the princes can use it in the future.

288
00:22:10,060 --> 00:22:12,620
Let’s leave this to the three ministries.

289
00:22:13,700 --> 00:22:14,900
Speaking of the three ministries,

290
00:22:15,300 --> 00:22:16,700
Bao Zheng has submitted another proposal

291
00:22:16,900 --> 00:22:18,820
to impeach Supervisor of Finance Song Qi.

292
00:22:24,100 --> 00:22:26,060
He impeached the then Supervisor of Finance

293
00:22:26,300 --> 00:22:28,540
Zhang Fangping several times a few months ago.

294
00:22:28,900 --> 00:22:31,340
= Song Xiang, courtesy name Gongxu, Wen Yanbo, courtesy name Kuanfu =
He said Zhang Fangping

295
00:22:31,660 --> 00:22:34,740
took advantage of his position

296
00:22:34,860 --> 00:22:36,460
while collecting liquor tax from Liu Baoheng

297
00:22:36,780 --> 00:22:38,980
and bought residences from Liu at reduced prices.

298
00:22:39,500 --> 00:22:42,060
He said Zhang Fangping is shameless

299
00:22:42,100 --> 00:22:43,260
and can’t be put in an important position.

300
00:22:45,100 --> 00:22:46,380
Zhang Fangping has been demoted,

301
00:22:46,660 --> 00:22:47,660
and Song Qi has taken over.

302
00:22:47,660 --> 00:22:48,940
But now he’s impeaching Song Qi? For what?

303
00:22:49,780 --> 00:22:51,380
Bao Zheng said

304
00:22:52,220 --> 00:22:54,780
Song Qi held a lot of banquets before,

305
00:22:54,860 --> 00:22:57,580
and let his family use government funds.

306
00:22:57,940 --> 00:23:01,260
He also said Song Qi is in charge of finance,

307
00:23:01,260 --> 00:23:03,220
and his brother Song Xiang is also in office.

308
00:23:03,380 --> 00:23:04,420
They hold too much power,

309
00:23:04,780 --> 00:23:06,460
and it’s bad to the country.

310
00:23:08,260 --> 00:23:11,780
I highly agree with Bao Zheng.

311
00:23:12,180 --> 00:23:12,860
Your Majesty...

312
00:23:15,540 --> 00:23:16,860
Zhang Fangping abused his position.

313
00:23:17,220 --> 00:23:20,220
Song Qi is also not qualified.

314
00:23:20,540 --> 00:23:22,860
Bao Zheng is simply stating the truth.

315
00:23:26,500 --> 00:23:27,580
But will there

316
00:23:27,900 --> 00:23:29,300
be a Supervisor of Finance

317
00:23:29,300 --> 00:23:30,820
that won’t get impeached by Bao Zheng?

318
00:23:31,820 --> 00:23:34,580
= Bao Zheng, courtesy name Xiren =

319
00:23:39,980 --> 00:23:41,940
Your Majesty hold a banquet

320
00:23:41,940 --> 00:23:42,980
to celebrate Madam Dong’s and Madam Zhou’s pregnancy.

321
00:23:42,980 --> 00:23:44,100
This is a very happy event.

322
00:23:44,260 --> 00:23:45,540
I feel honored to be invited

323
00:23:45,540 --> 00:23:48,100
and I’m supposed to congratulate you.

324
00:23:48,820 --> 00:23:49,540
However,

325
00:23:50,860 --> 00:23:52,740
I haven’t yet got a reply

326
00:23:52,740 --> 00:23:54,540
regarding my proposals.

327
00:23:54,540 --> 00:23:57,020
I’m very anxious.

328
00:23:58,020 --> 00:23:59,900
I’ve read your proposals.

329
00:24:01,140 --> 00:24:02,140
I agree with you.

330
00:24:03,740 --> 00:24:05,340
It’s true that Song Qi is not a good fit

331
00:24:05,940 --> 00:24:07,260
for the position of Supervisor of Finance.

332
00:24:09,780 --> 00:24:11,860
I’ve discussed this with several ministers

333
00:24:12,940 --> 00:24:14,740
and decided to send him away

334
00:24:15,100 --> 00:24:17,420
and let you take his place.

335
00:24:25,460 --> 00:24:26,340
Your Majesty!

336
00:24:29,540 --> 00:24:30,500
Your Majesty!

337
00:24:33,700 --> 00:24:34,460
I...

338
00:24:35,500 --> 00:24:38,500
I’m not coveting his position.

339
00:24:42,340 --> 00:24:46,100
I’m not joking.

340
00:24:54,860 --> 00:24:55,700
Your Majesty!

341
00:24:59,340 --> 00:25:02,660
= Hall of Peace =

342
00:25:02,940 --> 00:25:05,300
This pair of bracelets will bring prosperity.

343
00:25:10,140 --> 00:25:12,020
His Majesty is 50 this year,

344
00:25:12,220 --> 00:25:13,580
yet Madams can still

345
00:25:13,580 --> 00:25:14,780
get pregnant.

346
00:25:14,860 --> 00:25:16,340
It’s really amazing.

347
00:25:17,700 --> 00:25:18,940
Madams

348
00:25:19,180 --> 00:25:20,460
are also blessed.

349
00:25:21,020 --> 00:25:22,380
I went to buy some gifts immediately

350
00:25:22,380 --> 00:25:23,980
after I heard the news

351
00:25:23,980 --> 00:25:25,260
= Madam Zhou =
and came to congratulate you.

352
00:25:25,700 --> 00:25:28,020
I’ll bring you more when the princes are born.

353
00:25:29,460 --> 00:25:30,820
You’re too kind.

354
00:25:31,180 --> 00:25:32,860
You brought so many precious gifts.

355
00:25:34,580 --> 00:25:35,820
You two should thank her.

356
00:25:36,780 --> 00:25:37,980
Thank you for your gifts.

357
00:25:39,100 --> 00:25:40,620
You’re really good at selecting gifts.

358
00:25:40,820 --> 00:25:42,860
I like this bracelet very much.

359
00:25:43,020 --> 00:25:44,300
It can bring good fortune.

360
00:25:46,100 --> 00:25:48,060
It’s great that you like it.

361
00:25:48,860 --> 00:25:51,260
Otherwise, Princess will blame me

362
00:25:51,660 --> 00:25:53,420
for disgracing her in front of you.

363
00:25:54,260 --> 00:25:55,820
You’re too polite.

364
00:25:56,700 --> 00:25:58,220
When will His Majesty

365
00:25:58,220 --> 00:25:59,260
have a grandson?

366
00:25:59,620 --> 00:26:00,460
I’ll also

367
00:26:00,460 --> 00:26:01,740
prepare some precious gifts then.

368
00:26:06,380 --> 00:26:07,460
Princess is so shy.

369
00:26:11,020 --> 00:26:13,020
You’re really good at talking.

370
00:26:13,860 --> 00:26:14,580
How...

371
00:26:14,980 --> 00:26:17,020
How can a couple have a baby

372
00:26:17,220 --> 00:26:18,860
if they never touch each other?

373
00:26:29,180 --> 00:26:30,460
I also want to come here

374
00:26:30,700 --> 00:26:32,100
carrying a grandson.

375
00:26:32,940 --> 00:26:34,340
But Princess

376
00:26:34,340 --> 00:26:35,380
can’t possibly give birth

377
00:26:35,380 --> 00:26:36,700
to a baby by herself.

378
00:26:38,100 --> 00:26:41,060
It’d be bizarre if that happened

379
00:26:41,300 --> 00:26:43,060
since they never share the same bed.

380
00:26:44,860 --> 00:26:47,540
Even with the Heaven’s blessing,

381
00:26:48,060 --> 00:26:50,220
it won’t happen

382
00:26:50,420 --> 00:26:51,940
if Princess doesn’t want.

383
00:26:55,820 --> 00:26:56,620
Today,

384
00:26:56,660 --> 00:27:00,460
Mrs. Yang and Huirou came.

385
00:27:01,860 --> 00:27:03,420
I told the Empress yesterday

386
00:27:03,660 --> 00:27:05,660
to invite them have dinner here,

387
00:27:06,060 --> 00:27:08,380
and let Huirou stay in the palace

388
00:27:08,380 --> 00:27:09,300
for one more day.

389
00:27:12,420 --> 00:27:13,900
The two madams are pregnant,

390
00:27:14,180 --> 00:27:16,420
Huirou is going to be a sister.

391
00:27:18,060 --> 00:27:19,100
But when I

392
00:27:19,860 --> 00:27:21,260
prepared gifts

393
00:27:21,260 --> 00:27:22,340
for the unborn children,

394
00:27:22,340 --> 00:27:23,300
all I was thinking is

395
00:27:23,620 --> 00:27:25,420
Huirou might like this gift,

396
00:27:25,420 --> 00:27:27,420
or I should’ve given this gift to Huirou too.

397
00:27:29,020 --> 00:27:30,780
I suddenly remembered the days

398
00:27:30,900 --> 00:27:32,220
when you selected gifts

399
00:27:32,700 --> 00:27:34,700
and came up with a name for Princess

400
00:27:34,940 --> 00:27:36,300
before she was born.

401
00:27:41,420 --> 00:27:42,300
Look at me.

402
00:27:43,180 --> 00:27:44,620
This gift I prepared for Huirou

403
00:27:44,780 --> 00:27:45,940
is too childish for her.

404
00:27:50,700 --> 00:27:51,900
Seems I should keep it

405
00:27:52,100 --> 00:27:53,540
for my future granddaughter.

406
00:28:03,340 --> 00:28:04,180
Huirou,

407
00:28:07,020 --> 00:28:08,900
I know you don’t like Li Wei.

408
00:28:10,260 --> 00:28:11,660
But now

409
00:28:13,740 --> 00:28:15,300
you’re already his wife.

410
00:28:17,660 --> 00:28:18,500
How can you...

411
00:28:21,180 --> 00:28:23,140
You thought this through back then, right?

412
00:28:24,180 --> 00:28:25,780
What I thought through is

413
00:28:26,940 --> 00:28:28,140
that father raised me

414
00:28:28,900 --> 00:28:30,260
for almost 20 years.

415
00:28:31,380 --> 00:28:32,500
He must have his reasons

416
00:28:32,500 --> 00:28:33,380
not to let me

417
00:28:33,940 --> 00:28:35,260
marry the man I like.

418
00:28:37,620 --> 00:28:38,620
Since that’s the case,

419
00:28:39,300 --> 00:28:40,860
in order to console father,

420
00:28:41,260 --> 00:28:42,940
I’d marry anyone,

421
00:28:43,100 --> 00:28:45,020
no matter he’s old or young,

422
00:28:45,020 --> 00:28:46,100
a human being or an animal...

423
00:28:47,060 --> 00:28:47,900
Huirou!

424
00:28:54,460 --> 00:28:55,100
Huirou!

425
00:28:56,780 --> 00:28:58,380
Li Wei is your husband.

426
00:28:59,540 --> 00:29:00,980
You should share happiness and sorrow with him.

427
00:29:02,380 --> 00:29:03,860
How can you insult him like this?

428
00:29:06,380 --> 00:29:07,940
Do you still remember what you learnt

429
00:29:08,380 --> 00:29:09,540
from the books since you were young?

430
00:29:15,620 --> 00:29:16,660
You know what?

431
00:29:18,500 --> 00:29:19,820
The day I was married off to him,

432
00:29:20,980 --> 00:29:22,260
I told myself,

433
00:29:24,060 --> 00:29:24,860
fine,

434
00:29:26,620 --> 00:29:28,260
I’ll just give this body

435
00:29:28,300 --> 00:29:29,660
to Li Wei.

436
00:29:32,740 --> 00:29:33,940
But I couldn’t do it.

437
00:29:35,300 --> 00:29:37,460
What I learnt from the books

438
00:29:37,580 --> 00:29:38,420
stops me from

439
00:29:38,420 --> 00:29:39,780
lying on the same bed with him.

440
00:29:39,780 --> 00:29:40,780
It’d make me feel sick.

441
00:29:43,500 --> 00:29:44,540
Huirou,

442
00:29:53,290 --> 00:29:57,450
Li Wei might be common-looking,

443
00:29:59,290 --> 00:30:01,090
but he’s good at painting.

444
00:30:03,610 --> 00:30:05,890
And he’s very kind and honest.

445
00:30:08,090 --> 00:30:09,890
Do you still remember the first time

446
00:30:10,930 --> 00:30:12,450
you met him when you were a kid?

447
00:30:13,490 --> 00:30:14,490
You asked him for candied fruits...

448
00:30:14,490 --> 00:30:15,370
Don’t mention it.

449
00:30:23,530 --> 00:30:24,370
I can’t remember

450
00:30:24,370 --> 00:30:25,610
what he looked like at all.

451
00:30:27,410 --> 00:30:28,370
Right now,

452
00:30:30,210 --> 00:30:31,530
I only wish that

453
00:30:31,530 --> 00:30:32,690
he’d never touch me.

454
00:30:33,010 --> 00:30:33,850
Please.

455
00:30:33,850 --> 00:30:35,130
Please don’t mention

456
00:30:35,330 --> 00:30:36,210
this fat and ugly man

457
00:30:36,210 --> 00:30:37,170
who drools when sleeping

458
00:30:37,170 --> 00:30:38,330
once touched me before!

459
00:30:45,530 --> 00:30:46,370
Huirou,

460
00:30:49,970 --> 00:30:51,170
no one can live

461
00:30:51,170 --> 00:30:52,410
a perfect life.

462
00:30:54,450 --> 00:30:56,050
You’ve been loved by everyone since young.

463
00:30:56,570 --> 00:30:57,690
You’d rarely experienced the feeling

464
00:30:57,690 --> 00:30:58,770
of disappointment,

465
00:31:00,010 --> 00:31:02,090
but your marriage disappointed you a lot.

466
00:31:02,330 --> 00:31:03,690
I understand how you feel.

467
00:31:03,690 --> 00:31:04,450
However...

468
00:31:06,210 --> 00:31:06,810
No.

469
00:31:10,090 --> 00:31:13,370
You don’t understand.

470
00:31:15,810 --> 00:31:17,530
I’d only call it an imperfect life

471
00:31:17,970 --> 00:31:19,610
if I marry someone I like

472
00:31:19,610 --> 00:31:21,090
but he fails to meet my expectations.

473
00:31:24,010 --> 00:31:27,130
If I married Cao Ping back then,

474
00:31:28,330 --> 00:31:29,210
but he treated me badly,

475
00:31:29,490 --> 00:31:30,890
I’d follow your advice today.

476
00:31:32,370 --> 00:31:33,370
But that’s not the case.

477
00:31:36,730 --> 00:31:37,570
Your Highness,

478
00:31:42,690 --> 00:31:43,490
mother,

479
00:31:48,010 --> 00:31:49,170
you’d never understand

480
00:31:49,170 --> 00:31:50,090
how I feel.

481
00:31:54,210 --> 00:31:55,730
The only thing you want

482
00:31:55,730 --> 00:31:57,530
is to be favored by father.

483
00:31:59,890 --> 00:32:00,650
But for me,

484
00:32:02,930 --> 00:32:04,250
what I want is...

485
00:32:13,130 --> 00:32:14,730
If there’s something I want,

486
00:32:16,090 --> 00:32:17,370
it’d be that

487
00:32:18,130 --> 00:32:19,930
Li Wei can’t come to eat with me today

488
00:32:19,930 --> 00:32:21,330
because his friends come to visit him

489
00:32:21,330 --> 00:32:22,890
or he has to attend to his business.

490
00:32:30,850 --> 00:32:33,690
But he doesn’t have many friends,

491
00:32:34,250 --> 00:32:36,050
and he doesn’t have urgent business.

492
00:32:37,370 --> 00:32:38,530
So he’d have dinner with me

493
00:32:38,530 --> 00:32:39,570
every day,

494
00:32:42,610 --> 00:32:43,690
and what I can do is

495
00:32:43,690 --> 00:32:44,770
trying not to look at him.

496
00:32:50,250 --> 00:32:51,690
Father only married me off to him

497
00:32:52,930 --> 00:32:53,970
to bring honor

498
00:32:53,970 --> 00:32:55,250
to Empress Dowager Zhangyi’s family.

499
00:32:58,170 --> 00:32:59,850
So the day I married him,

500
00:33:01,410 --> 00:33:02,930
this goal was already achieved.

501
00:33:04,610 --> 00:33:06,770
They’re more closely linked to our imperial family,

502
00:33:08,250 --> 00:33:09,130
and Li Wei

503
00:33:10,130 --> 00:33:11,370
will be able to enjoy his whole life

504
00:33:11,370 --> 00:33:13,650
with the title of Prince Consort.

505
00:33:22,410 --> 00:33:23,610
I’m not a man.

506
00:33:24,690 --> 00:33:25,410
So it’s not my responsibility

507
00:33:25,410 --> 00:33:27,010
to continue our family’s bloodline.

508
00:33:28,530 --> 00:33:30,290
And Li Wei can take concubines.

509
00:33:30,290 --> 00:33:31,530
He can have as many women

510
00:33:31,530 --> 00:33:33,130
and children as he wants.

511
00:33:34,130 --> 00:33:35,890
He can still have progeny without me.

512
00:33:38,370 --> 00:33:39,090
In the future,

513
00:33:40,410 --> 00:33:42,930
if his concubines give birth,

514
00:33:43,290 --> 00:33:44,890
I will treat their kids as my own,

515
00:33:44,890 --> 00:33:46,770
and ask father to promote them.

516
00:33:59,690 --> 00:34:00,490
No.

517
00:34:02,610 --> 00:34:03,370
No.

518
00:34:06,290 --> 00:34:07,090
Huirou,

519
00:34:10,210 --> 00:34:11,210
I didn’t...

520
00:34:35,850 --> 00:34:36,730
Father.

521
00:34:57,610 --> 00:34:58,290
Father.

522
00:34:59,930 --> 00:35:03,090
Please issue a decree

523
00:35:03,810 --> 00:35:05,770
allowing Li Wei to take concubines.

524
00:35:07,290 --> 00:35:09,690
I’ll be a good daughter to you

525
00:35:11,050 --> 00:35:12,450
and a good mother to Li Wei’s children

526
00:35:13,370 --> 00:35:15,450
in this lifetime.

527
00:35:35,630 --> 00:35:37,660
On the occasion of the funeral
of Lord Zhao Yunrang,

528
00:35:37,660 --> 00:35:38,750
His Majesty will not hold court for five days.

529
00:35:38,750 --> 00:35:41,880
Yunrang will be given the title of Prince of Pu.

530
00:35:51,980 --> 00:35:54,640
The title of Prince of Pu?

531
00:35:55,100 --> 00:35:57,080
His Majesty really holds Yunrang in high esteem.

532
00:35:57,530 --> 00:35:58,680
Anyway,

533
00:35:59,200 --> 00:36:01,640
Yunrang is the birth father of Zongshi.

534
00:36:06,850 --> 00:36:08,430
Although there’s a good chance

535
00:36:10,550 --> 00:36:12,270
His Majesty will have a son,

536
00:36:14,700 --> 00:36:16,300
he still treats Zongshi

537
00:36:17,050 --> 00:36:17,750
very differently

538
00:36:17,750 --> 00:36:19,350
from how he treats other imperial relatives.

539
00:36:32,580 --> 00:36:33,500
Yunrang,

540
00:36:35,470 --> 00:36:38,910
you can rest in peace.

541
00:36:40,970 --> 00:36:42,360
Your life was smooth,

542
00:36:43,270 --> 00:36:44,410
you were kind to others,

543
00:36:45,320 --> 00:36:46,910
you were blessed with many children,

544
00:36:48,870 --> 00:36:50,490
= Zhao Zongshi =
and your children are very capable,

545
00:36:51,600 --> 00:36:52,860
especially Zongshi.

546
00:36:53,720 --> 00:36:55,160
He’s filial and righteous,

547
00:36:55,670 --> 00:36:56,890
clever and hardworking.

548
00:36:59,520 --> 00:37:02,910
I envy you very much.

549
00:37:10,680 --> 00:37:11,440
Did you really show it

550
00:37:11,460 --> 00:37:12,780
to Mr. Cui Bai?

551
00:37:15,300 --> 00:37:16,140
He said it’s good?

552
00:37:17,220 --> 00:37:18,660
I dare not lie to you.

553
00:37:19,300 --> 00:37:21,420
Qiuhe’s family was back in the Capital.

554
00:37:21,620 --> 00:37:23,420
So I took this painting with me

555
00:37:23,540 --> 00:37:25,260
when I went out to do New Year’s shopping

556
00:37:25,380 --> 00:37:26,980
and paid a visit to Qiuhe’s family.

557
00:37:27,780 --> 00:37:29,860
Qiuhe spoke highly of it,

558
00:37:30,300 --> 00:37:31,660
and then showed it to Mr. Cui.

559
00:37:32,100 --> 00:37:33,900
At the time, Mr. Guo,

560
00:37:33,900 --> 00:37:35,420
one of Mr. Cui’s friends, was also there.

561
00:37:35,580 --> 00:37:36,700
He also said it’s good.

562
00:37:45,740 --> 00:37:46,860
If you don’t show your talent

563
00:37:46,860 --> 00:37:47,820
to Princess,

564
00:37:49,220 --> 00:37:50,460
of course there will be no chance

565
00:37:50,460 --> 00:37:51,540
for her to fall for you.

566
00:37:52,980 --> 00:37:54,260
With all due respect,

567
00:37:55,100 --> 00:37:56,020
I also thought

568
00:37:56,020 --> 00:37:57,460
you’re not worthy of Princess.

569
00:37:59,060 --> 00:37:59,940
But now,

570
00:38:00,860 --> 00:38:02,420
I truly hope you and Princess

571
00:38:02,420 --> 00:38:03,580
could love each other,

572
00:38:05,460 --> 00:38:07,740
make paintings

573
00:38:08,500 --> 00:38:09,860
and appreciate paintings together,

574
00:38:11,820 --> 00:38:13,580
and have a lovely baby

575
00:38:13,580 --> 00:38:14,860
as soon as possible.

576
00:38:22,780 --> 00:38:24,100
You lost.

577
00:38:25,060 --> 00:38:25,940
We agreed that

578
00:38:26,260 --> 00:38:27,140
if you lose,

579
00:38:27,540 --> 00:38:29,020
you’ll give me a gift.

580
00:38:39,820 --> 00:38:42,700
But I only learnt

581
00:38:42,820 --> 00:38:44,700
some basic techniques

582
00:38:44,700 --> 00:38:45,780
when you learnt how to paint.

583
00:38:46,260 --> 00:38:47,260
I paint very badly.

584
00:38:47,900 --> 00:38:49,500
I can’t make the painting for your screen.

585
00:38:50,820 --> 00:38:52,580
I won’t show it to others.

586
00:38:53,460 --> 00:38:54,420
I think the paintings made by you

587
00:38:54,820 --> 00:38:55,900
are the best.

588
00:38:57,460 --> 00:38:58,460
I can have you around

589
00:38:58,860 --> 00:39:00,180
when I’m awake.

590
00:39:01,220 --> 00:39:03,900
But when it’s time to sleep,

591
00:39:04,420 --> 00:39:05,900
Jiaqing Zi and Xiao Ye’er

592
00:39:06,180 --> 00:39:07,220
will take your place.

593
00:39:09,020 --> 00:39:11,820
It’d be great if I can have

594
00:39:12,300 --> 00:39:13,220
your painting by my side.

595
00:39:18,900 --> 00:39:20,740
Princess, I...

596
00:39:26,420 --> 00:39:27,860
If you want a picture for the screen,

597
00:39:28,220 --> 00:39:30,180
I’ll buy a painting made by a famous artist.

598
00:39:33,140 --> 00:39:34,340
I’ll say it again.

599
00:39:36,460 --> 00:39:38,340
I want to fall asleep
with your painting by my side.

600
00:39:40,820 --> 00:39:41,740
When I wake up,

601
00:39:42,060 --> 00:39:43,420
I want to see the painting made by you.

602
00:39:44,220 --> 00:39:45,060
Only in that way

603
00:39:50,340 --> 00:39:53,460
will I feel less desperate

604
00:39:55,060 --> 00:39:56,100
and less scared.

605
00:40:48,860 --> 00:40:49,620
Prince Consort.

606
00:40:49,740 --> 00:40:50,580
You’re lying.

607
00:40:51,580 --> 00:40:52,420
You’re lying.

608
00:40:53,500 --> 00:40:55,180
She’s never going to like me.

609
00:40:55,260 --> 00:40:56,180
Don’t tear it up.

610
00:40:56,180 --> 00:40:56,980
You’re lying.

611
00:40:57,940 --> 00:40:58,820
No matter what,

612
00:40:59,140 --> 00:41:00,580
she’s not going to like me.

613
00:41:02,860 --> 00:41:04,260
Princess doesn’t like this painting?

614
00:41:04,260 --> 00:41:05,540
There’s someone she loves.

615
00:41:06,100 --> 00:41:08,100
She was in love with someone all along.

616
00:41:11,460 --> 00:41:12,260
Don’t tear it up.

617
00:41:16,700 --> 00:41:18,620
She would rather choose that eunuch.

618
00:41:20,580 --> 00:41:22,380
She had feelings for that eunuch all along.

619
00:41:23,260 --> 00:41:24,860
He is always by her side.

620
00:41:25,420 --> 00:41:26,900
I should have noticed this earlier.

621
00:41:30,140 --> 00:41:31,140
It’s been so many years.

622
00:41:33,100 --> 00:41:34,460
Every time I went to the palace

623
00:41:34,940 --> 00:41:36,500
to see Princess,

624
00:41:37,900 --> 00:41:39,460
he was by her side.

625
00:41:40,620 --> 00:41:42,260
I should have noticed this earlier.

626
00:41:45,900 --> 00:41:47,380
I should have noticed this earlier!

627
00:42:01,100 --> 00:42:02,220
Count the gifts in the carriage,

628
00:42:02,460 --> 00:42:03,580
and move them to the warehouse.

629
00:42:04,060 --> 00:42:05,020
You must be careful.

630
00:42:05,020 --> 00:42:06,100
Don’t miss anything.

631
00:42:06,340 --> 00:42:07,060
Yes.

632
00:42:12,260 --> 00:42:13,180
Princess went outside.

633
00:42:14,180 --> 00:42:14,980
She went outside?

634
00:42:16,020 --> 00:42:17,300
To where? With whom?

635
00:42:17,300 --> 00:42:17,980
For what?

636
00:42:17,980 --> 00:42:19,380
= Xiao Ye’er =

637
00:42:19,380 --> 00:42:20,420
Princess always wanted to go out

638
00:42:20,420 --> 00:42:21,420
to watch the lanterns on the streets.

639
00:42:21,820 --> 00:42:23,460
She put on a veil and went out

640
00:42:23,460 --> 00:42:25,180
with Jiaqing Zi just now.

641
00:42:25,580 --> 00:42:26,380
Princess said

642
00:42:26,420 --> 00:42:27,860
she’s going to Winehouse Fan tonight,

643
00:42:28,100 --> 00:42:29,260
and you should go there to meet her.

644
00:42:46,320 --> 00:42:53,280
♪ Memory is the breath of deep sleep ♪

645
00:42:53,840 --> 00:43:00,760
♪ It emerges in every crevice ♪

646
00:43:01,240 --> 00:43:07,600
♪ Shallow dreams are like
copper bells under eaves ♪

647
00:43:08,040 --> 00:43:14,800
♪ Woken up when the wind blows ♪

648
00:43:16,040 --> 00:43:22,840
♪ Fate is predetermined ♪

649
00:43:23,440 --> 00:43:30,160
♪ Struggle to break out of it ♪

650
00:43:30,720 --> 00:43:37,760
♪ Who will battle fate with me ♪

651
00:43:37,760 --> 00:43:44,600
♪ Regardless of the ending ♪

652
00:43:49,480 --> 00:43:53,000
♪ Peach branches shake in the spring breeze ♪

653
00:43:53,200 --> 00:43:56,800
♪ Walls sigh, the wind is silent ♪

654
00:43:56,800 --> 00:44:00,000
♪ The boy beside the wall is unaware of it ♪

655
00:44:00,000 --> 00:44:04,400
♪ He plays with the butterfly, gathering honey ♪

656
00:44:04,400 --> 00:44:08,120
♪ Peach blossoms tell a love story ♪

657
00:44:08,120 --> 00:44:11,680
♪ About a couple who lives happily ♪

658
00:44:11,680 --> 00:44:15,400
♪ Unluckily deep love comes to nowhere ♪

659
00:44:15,400 --> 00:44:21,160
♪ All fated,
drawing Double Happiness in autumn ♪

